  <p>
    <strong>Note:</strong> Actual throughput depends on oil viscosity and process temperature. Higher temperatures reduce viscosity and allow higher flow rates. <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/">Contact us</a> for sizing on your specific cutting oil.
  </p>

